{
  "texts": [
    "The advantages of this setup are: 1) the standard TSN architecture is easy to implement and reproducible as it is off-the-shelf in Ten-sorFlow and PyTorch, and 2) we intend to apply transfer learning for Fusion MLP, whereby a standard architecture makes transfer learning easier.",
    "We have adapted the MMAction2foot_1 interface for using TSN as a feature extractor.",
    "Audio streamFor audio with a duration of t seconds, we convert it into an image-based representation.",
    "This results in a 299 Â 299 image-based representation, referred to as an audio-image of the whole action data sample.",
    "This audio-image is then fed as an input to the IRV2 backbone."
  ]
